data.meta_description:
2 likes, 0 comments - firozeshakir on May 25, 2024: "Black Jesus of Bandra

Yeshu Masih 
Was born 
Uneccesarily he died 
For the sins of Man. 
He was crucified
He loved Mary Magdalene 
Her love he sacrificed 
If he had married
She would have been 
His bride his mentor. 
His guide.. A few chubby children besides 
But the Jews Philistines 
Took him for a ride 
On the cross 
He invoked his Father 
Forgive them mother fu****s 
he cried.ï¿½

#beggarpoet 
dedicated to Kazantakis".
